description: The Gucci Slip-On Model E is a statement piece for those who appreciate bold fashion choices. Made from sumptuous velvet, these slip-ons exude opulence and style. The vibrant red color adds a pop of color to your look. Available in US size 9, these slip-ons offer a comfortable and easy fit. Make a fashion-forward statement with this eye-catching piece from the renowned Gucci Boutique.
